---
import SectionWrapper from '../SectionWrapper.astro';
import Button from '../Button.astro';
---
<SectionWrapper id="cost" theme="dark">
  <!-- Section label -->
  <p class="section-label">// 08 COST OF WAITING</p>

  <!-- Headline -->
  <h2 class="cost-headline">
    <span>You're already paying for this.</span>
    <span>There's just no invoice for it yet.</span>
  </h2>

  <!-- Body copy -->
  <div class="cost-body" data-animate>
    <p>
      That slow month. That competitor who keeps winning work you know you
      could do better. That referral who visited your site and never called
      back. There's no line item for any of it. But the cost is real and it
      compounds.
    </p>

    <p>
      Every day without a working system is a day you're paying the
      fragmentation tax. Copy-pasting between tools. Re-answering the same
      intake questions. Rebuilding the same follow-up from scratch. That time
      is already gone.
    </p>

    <p>
      Word-of-mouth works until it stops. When it does, there's nothing
      underneath it. The person who found your site, saw nothing that made
      them confident, and called your competitor instead. That cost never
      shows up on a statement.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Terminal stat block -->
  <div class="cost-stats" data-animate>
    <dl>
      <div class="stat-line">
        <dt class="stat-label stat-danger">&gt; DAILY TIME LOST TO TOOL SWITCHING (avg, per owner):</dt>
        <dd class="stat-value stat-danger">~1.5 hrs</dd>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-line">
        <dt class="stat-label stat-danger">&gt; PER WEEK:</dt>
        <dd class="stat-value stat-danger">~7.5 hrs</dd>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-line">
        <dt class="stat-label stat-danger">&gt; PER YEAR:</dt>
        <dd class="stat-value stat-danger">~47 work days</dd>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-line">
        <dt class="stat-label stat-danger">&gt; OWNERS WHO'VE LOST SIGNIFICANT INCOME TO INEFFICIENT SYSTEMS:</dt>
        <dd class="stat-value stat-danger">42%</dd>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-line">
        <dt class="stat-label stat-danger">&gt; OWNERS CONFIDENT THEIR MARKETING WORKS:</dt>
        <dd class="stat-value stat-danger">1 in 5</dd>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-line stat-line-positive">
        <dt class="stat-label stat-success">&gt; COST TO DIAGNOSE:</dt>
        <dd class="stat-value stat-success">$0.00</dd>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-line">
        <dt class="stat-label stat-compounding">&gt; COST TO DO NOTHING:</dt>
        <dd class="stat-value stat-compounding">compounding</dd>
      </div>
    </dl>
    <p class="stat-source">// Slack / Salesforce, 2024 · Simply Business, 2025, n=1,023 · Constant Contact / Ascend2, 2025</p>
  </div>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <div class="cost-cta">
    <Button variant="ghost" href="/diagnostic">[GET YOUR FREE DIAGNOSTIC &gt;]</Button>
    <Button variant="primary" href="#diagnostic">[START YOUR PROJECT &gt;]</Button>
  </div>
</SectionWrapper>

<style>
  /* Headline - Geist Sans */
  .cost-headline {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--step-4);
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-snug);
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
  }

  .cost-headline span {
    display: block;
  }

  .cost-headline span:first-child {
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .cost-headline span:last-child {
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  /* Body copy */
  .cost-body {
    max-width: var(--measure-normal);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }

  .cost-body p {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--step-0);
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .cost-body p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* Glass stat block */
  .cost-stats {
    background: oklch(0.20 0.09 62 / 0.6);
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    border: 1px solid oklch(1 0 0 / 0.08);
    border-radius: var(--radius-panel);
    padding: var(--space-8);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-feature-settings: 'tnum' 1;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
    max-width: var(--measure-normal);
  }

  .stat-line {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    padding: var(--space-1) 0;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .stat-line-positive {
    margin-top: var(--space-3);
    padding-top: var(--space-3);
    border-top: 1px solid oklch(1 0 0 / 0.10);
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: var(--step--2);
  }

  .stat-value {
    font-size: var(--step--2);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-align: right;
  }

  .stat-danger {
    color: var(--error);
  }

  .stat-value.stat-danger {
    text-shadow: 0 0 12px oklch(0.65 0.25 25 / 0.5);
  }

  .stat-success {
    color: var(--success);
  }

  .stat-value.stat-success {
    text-shadow: 0 0 12px oklch(0.70 0.20 145 / 0.5);
  }

  .stat-compounding {
    color: var(--warning);
  }

  .stat-value.stat-compounding {
    text-shadow: 0 0 12px oklch(0.75 0.18 85 / 0.5);
  }

  .stat-source {
    font-size: var(--step--2);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-top: var(--space-3);
    padding-top: var(--space-3);
    border-top: 1px solid oklch(1 0 0 / 0.10);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* CTA area */
  .cost-cta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .cost-headline {
      font-size: var(--step-3);
    }

    .stat-line {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: var(--space-1);
    }

    .stat-value {
      text-align: left;
    }

    .cost-cta {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .cost-headline {
      font-size: var(--step-2);
    }
  }
</style>
